1254
01:21:49.958 --> 01:21:50.957
You touch another piece of my--

1255
01:21:50.958 --> 01:21:52.499
- Enough.
- Take the "mole" out of it.

1256
01:21:52.500 --> 01:21:53.790
- It's Mr. Elder to you.
