Johnny. don't be mad.
I didn't dress you.

1260
01:22:00.708 --> 01:22:02.540
Don't listen to him.
You're handsome.

1261
01:22:03.833 --> 01:22:05.040
Harvey.

1262
01:22:05.041 --> 01:22:06.958
I'm sorry. Sue. I'm...

1263
