1271
01:22:37.375 --> 01:22:38.750
Hello there.

1272
01:22:39.333 --> 01:22:41.290
Welcome. sunshiners.

1273
01:22:41.291 --> 01:22:42.708
Thank you so much.

1274
01:22:43.750 --> 01:22:47.415
